statements: SELECT * FROM STEM_Projects WHERE project_id = 1;
SELECT project_name, progress FROM STEM_Projects WHERE start_date > '2021-01-01';
SELECT project_name, project_description FROM STEM_Projects WHERE progress > 50;
SELECT project_name, student_id FROM STEM_Projects ORDER BY project_id DESC;
SELECT * FROM STEM_Projects WHERE end_date <= '2022-01-01';
SELECT project_name, progress FROM STEM_Projects WHERE progress > 50 ORDER BY progress DESC LIMIT 5
SELECT * FROM STEM_Projects WHERE start_date <= '2022-01-01' AND end_date >= '2022-12-31' ORDER BY project_name ASC
SELECT project_id, project_name, start_date, end_date FROM STEM_Projects WHERE student_id = 12345 AND progress BETWEEN 25 AND 75 ORDER BY start_date DESC
SELECT project_name, project_description FROM STEM_Projects WHERE progress = 100 ORDER BY project_name ASC, project_description DESC LIMIT 10
SELECT project_name AS 'Project Name', start_date AS 'Start Date' FROM STEM_Projects WHERE progress < 50 ORDER BY start_date ASC, project_name DESC LIMIT 3
SELECT * FROM Projects;
SELECT project_name, project_start_date FROM Projects;
SELECT project_id, project_name, project_end_date FROM Projects ORDER BY project_end_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM Competitions WHERE competition_location = 'New York';
SELECT competition_name, competition_date FROM Competitions ORDER BY competition_date ASC;
SELECT project_id, project_name, project_description, project_start_date, project_end_date FROM Projects;
SELECT project_id, project_name, project_start_date FROM Projects WHERE project_start_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT project_name, COUNT(*) AS project_count FROM Projects GROUP BY project_name;
SELECT competition_name, competition_location, competition_date FROM Competitions ORDER BY competition_date DESC;
SELECT project_id, project_name, project_start_date FROM Projects WHERE project_start_date < '2022-06-01' ORDER BY project_start_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM projects;
SELECT project_id, project_name, project_status FROM projects;
SELECT project_name, project_description FROM projects WHERE project_status='Active';
SELECT project_id, project_name FROM projects ORDER BY project_name DESC;
SELECT project_id, student_id, project_status FROM projects WHERE project_status='In Progress' ORDER BY project_id ASC;
SELECT project_id, project_name, student_id, project_description, project_status FROM projects WHERE project_status = 'In Progress';
SELECT project_name, project_status FROM projects WHERE student_id = 123 ORDER BY project_name DESC;
SELECT competition_name, start_date, end_date, location FROM competitions WHERE location LIKE '%California%' ORDER BY start_date ASC;
SELECT project_name, role FROM projects JOIN project_participants ON projects.project_id = project_participants.project_id WHERE role = 'Leader';
SELECT project_name, student_id, role FROM projects JOIN project_participants ON projects.project_id = project_participants.project_id WHERE student_id = 456 ORDER BY project_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM Projects;
SELECT project_name, project_status FROM Projects WHERE project_status = 'In Progress';
SELECT project_name, student_id FROM Projects ORDER BY student_id DESC;
SELECT * FROM Students JOIN Projects ON Students.student_id = Projects.student_id;

SELECT project_name, competition_name FROM Projects JOIN Project_Competitions ON Projects.project_id = Project_Competitions.project_id JOIN Competitions ON Project_Competitions.competition_id = Competitions.competition_id;
SELECT * FROM Projects WHERE project_status = 'In Progress';
SELECT project_name, project_description FROM Projects WHERE project_id = 1;
SELECT project_name, student_name, grade_level FROM Projects p JOIN Students s ON p.student_id = s.student_id;
SELECT project_name, competition_name, competition_date FROM Projects p JOIN Project_Competitions pc ON p.project_id = pc.project_id JOIN Competitions c ON pc.competition_id = c.competition_id;

SELECT project_name, project_description, competition_name, location FROM Projects p JOIN Project_Competitions pc ON p.project_id = pc.project_id JOIN Competitions c ON pc.competition_id = c.competition_id WHERE grade_level > 10;
SELECT * FROM STEM_Projects;
SELECT project_name, project_category FROM STEM_Projects WHERE project_status = 'completed';
SELECT student_name, student_grade FROM Students ORDER BY student_grade DESC;
SELECT competition_name, competition_location FROM Competitions WHERE competition_date >= '2022-01-01';

SELECT project_name, student_name, competition_name FROM STEM_Projects JOIN Projects_Participants ON STEM_Projects.project_id = Projects_Participants.project_id JOIN Students ON Projects_Participants.student_id = Students.student_id JOIN Winners ON STEM_Projects.project_id = Winners.project_id AND Students.student_id = Winners.student_id JOIN Competitions ON Winners.competition_id = Competitions.competition_id WHERE Winners.prize = '1st Place';
SELECT * FROM STEM_Projects LIMIT 5;
SELECT project_name, project_category, project_status FROM STEM_Projects WHERE project_status = 'ongoing';
SELECT project_name, project_description FROM STEM_Projects WHERE project_id BETWEEN 1 AND 3;
SELECT project_category, COUNT(*) AS project_count FROM STEM_Projects GROUP BY project_category;

SELECT Students.student_name, Projects_Participants.project_id, Projects_Participants.student_id FROM Students INNER JOIN Projects_Participants ON Students.student_id = Projects_Participants.student_id ORDER BY Students.student_name ASC LIMIT 5;
